review_blob:
The pour is an incredible dark black with a half inch tan head that dissipates quickly. The smell is phenominal, chocolate, coffee and malty. The taste of this beer was beyond my expectations (which were high). Heavy chocolate taste laced with coffee and a great aftertaste. One of the best imperial stouts i've ever tried.
